{
  "stem": "1029.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we bought gas motorcyclists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we-- when we finally got home, it was so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We-- we went right away to see if anybody found the jewelry that we dug away, because on [INAUDIBLE], my grandfather had a jewelry store.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't find out about-- didn't even really think about my father until 1948, when I discovered that my mother had a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told my mother that, why does she do this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father could come home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's not done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother told me that there's no hope for my father to come through, because everybody froze when the Russians broke through that line around the dawn in [INAUDIBLE] line.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I cried for awhile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then that's when I realized that my father wasn't going to come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was getting older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother put me in a children's home, very religious, [INAUDIBLE] in Budapest, where-- [LAUGHS] where I helped out in the kitchen detail.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we-- every Saturday, they picked up our [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you know the warmed up beans, and the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a huge cauldron of [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] with [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], like an iceberg floating in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only the tip is a little bit, but the rest was all underneath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we picked this up, you know, from the baker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stopped under the tree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the four of us, we looked at this [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] floating in this beautiful mess of [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you know, that we picked up for 50 kids, don't forget.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Make a long story short, we took it back into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a big scream, and huge cry out of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they grabbed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were grounded for about a week, I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't get any [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't get any of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't get any of that for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's the story of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then from there, I go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us out-- they wanted to take us to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to us to make the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother got worried because at that time, you know, when the train-- when the boats were going to Israel, they were being sunk you know, by British, by Turks, by this or that, you know?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother said, don't go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Go with your-- with your uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go to Vienna or go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then maybe he'll take you out to Canada, because I'll be going to Canada.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'll be-- I'll-- you'll meet your mother in Canada.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SIGH]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
